Ibtissam Bouharat (Arabic; amụrụ na 2 Jenụwarị 1990) bụ onye na agba bọọlụ nke na agba dịka onye na eme egwuregwu netiti KV Malines
A mụrụ ya na Belgium, ọ na anọchite anya otu ụmụ nwanyị nke mba Morocco.
Bouharat malitere ọrụ ya na Dilbeek Sport
N'afọ 2005, ọ gara Brussels iji sonye na RSC Anderlecht wee malite ọrụ ọkachamara ya, site nebe ahụ
Ọ kwagara ọzọ noge ọkọchị nke afọ 2006 na KV Mechelen
N'ime afọ atọ na Mechelen, Bouharat agafeghị ịnọdụ ala na bench dị ka onye na agba bọọlụ
Nke ahụ mere ka ọ gaa nụzọ dị iche iji sonye na klọb ọhụrụ, DVK Haacht
Noge ọkọchị nke afọ 2010, ọ kwụsịrị igwu egwu na Tweede Klasse wee gaa otu afọ igwu egwu maka Eva's Tienen
Na 25 Mee 2011 ya na Romelu Lukaku, Vadis Odjidja, Faris Haroun na François Kompany gbara bọọlụ ọrụ ebere megide Racism
Ọ gbara bọọlụ ruo 30 June 2011 na Tienen wee sonye na ngalaba bọọlụ ụmụ nwanyị nke Lierse SK
Kemgbe 20 Mee 2012 ọ nọ nokpuru nkwekọrịta na Standard Liège
Mgbe Bouharat gbara bọọlụ na egwuregwu 13 na goolu 2 maka Standard Feminina, ọ hapụrụ Liège wee kwaga RSC Anderlecht na Brussels.
